OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBrewdog flouted US laws    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fover beer imports          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Scottish beer giant Brewdog sent       
OL,6, multiple shipments of beer to the US,  
OL,7, in contravention of US federal laws, a 
OL,8, BBC investigation has found.           
OL,10,FStaff at its Ellon brewery told the BBC
OL,11,Fthey were put under pressure in 2016   
OL,12,Fand 2017 to ship beer with ingredients 
OL,13,Fthat had not been legally approved.    
OL,15,FOne US-based importer said they had    
OL,16,Fbeen deceived by Brewdog.              
OL,18,FIn a social media post on Wednesday,   
OL,19,FBrewdog CEO James Watt admitted to     
OL,20,F"taking shortcuts" with the process.   
